What is an abstract class ?????
Abstract class ek aisi class hoti hai jiska object directly create nahi kar sakte.
Isme abstract methods (without body) aur normal methods dono ho sakte hain.
Iska use abstraction achieve karne aur common behavior define karne ke liye hota hai.
